name: Number of visits for the past 28 days
description: Analysis of the traffic created over the past month can be compared to the previous reports to reflect trends and improve the website. A result of 0 visits created over the past month indicates a technical issue or a faulty measurement of the data.

blocks.description: Checks the number of visits in past 28 days, if there are no visits, it fails
blocks.failHowtofix: Check, if the ATI measurement is set up correctly on your website.
